                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210718-105-off604 t18210718-105-crimeloc606"></join>; the constable asked if I missed any thing - I felt and missed my handkerchief. I went back with him, and he collared the prisoner and another boy, and took the handkerchief from his pocket.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210718-105-person968">
                  JAMES 
                  METCALF
               <interp inst="t18210718-105-person968" type="surname" value="METCALF"></interp>
