                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I saw the prisoner and another following a gentleman; they went into the crowd and followed Chadley, he nudged the boy - they turned back. I went and asked if he lost any thing, he missed his handkerchief. I went and took it out of the prisoner's pocket.</p>
